  <brief_title>Case Series Assessing TissuGlu速 Surgical Adhesive in Flap Surgery for Decubitus Repair</brief_title>
  <official_title>Post-Market, Investigator Initiated, Retrospective, Audited Observational Case Series Assessing a Lysine-Derived Urethane Adhesive (TissuGlu速 Surgical Adhesive) in Flap Surgery for Decubitus Repair</official_title>
